Sentencas: The impact of biomass-derived contaminants on solid-oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) with Ni/gadolinia-doped ceria (GDC) anodes was investigated using electrochemical impedance analysis.
Titulo: Impact of Biomass-Derived contaminants on SOFCs with Ni/Gadolinia-doped ceria anodes

Sentencas: Measurements were carried out with symmetric test cells under a single-gas atmosphere.
Titulo: Impact of Biomass-Derived contaminants on SOFCs with Ni/Gadolinia-doped ceria anodes

Sentencas: The impact of H2S, HCl, and naphthalene in the gas stream on the performance of Ni/GDC anodes are presented.
Titulo: Impact of Biomass-Derived contaminants on SOFCs with Ni/Gadolinia-doped ceria anodes

Sentencas: No significant impact has been observed up to 9 ppm H2S and HCl and 110 ppm naphthalene.
Titulo: Impact of Biomass-Derived contaminants on SOFCs with Ni/Gadolinia-doped ceria anodes
